trans-unit.source: Use the `CallTarget` element in your project file to create and execute this task.
For usage and parameter information, see [CallTarget Task](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.CallTarget"></xref> class.
Instructs the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine to build one or more targets in the current project.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if all targets built successfully; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

Gets or sets a Boolean value that indicates whether the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once per target (<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>) or the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once to build all targets (<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>).

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once per target; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once to build all targets.
Gets the outputs of all built targets.
The outputs of all built targets.
Gets or sets the target or targets to build.
The target or targets to build.
Gets or sets a Boolean value that indicates whether the MSBuild engine will return the built targets from the cache.
The scope of built targets in the cash is (ProjectFileName, GlobalProperties)[TargetNames] as a list of build items.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the MSBuild engine will return the built targets from the cache; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
